title: Music Maniak - 17 Unfinished FL Studio Projects
description:
This is a collection of 17 FL Studio Projects I did around 2007/ early 2008. Some songs were just started and only contain a few notes, and other projects were as good as finished. For your ease, I included both an mp3 and a zipped loop file of every song, which you can open in FL Studio 8. If you find a project of interest to you, don&#039;t hesitate to finish it or remix it or whatever, I would love to hear the result though and some credits would be nice! Hey, I gave you the opportunity to think of the title already, unless you&#039;re into dates...! ;)

So what genres can you expect:

Electronica
Soft Rock
Trance
Techno
RnB (rarely)

You can find rules and contact details in the readme.txt file within the download.

So what are you waiting for, start remixing! ;)
